You must first download mythtv source code before attempting to compile this plugin. (https://github.com/MythTV/mythtv)
You must also have installed Pianod before attempting to run this plugin (http://deviousfish.com/pianod/)

Once mythtv is compiled, then download the plugin and move it to mythtv/mythplugins/

run:
 qmake
 make
 sudo make install


In one of your UI files (mainmenu.xml), add the following:

<button>
   <type>PANDORA_MYTH</type>
   <text>Pandora Myth</text>
   <action>PLUGIN mythpianod</action>
</button>

Or run install.pl that attempts to perform the above action automatically.
